<section class="section-padding" style="background-color: var(--color-bg);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>{{ section.settings.title | default: 'Awareness That Stays With You' }}</h2>
      <p>{{ section.settings.subtitle | default: "PostureTru isn't designed to force perfect posture. It's designed to help you notice the exact moment you begin to slouch, so better posture becomes something you naturally return to, day after day." }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-4">
      <!-- Benefit 1 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <h3>Notice the Moment</h3>
        <p>The hardest part about improving posture is realizing when you've lost it. PostureTru gently vibrates the moment you begin to slouch, bringing your attention back without interrupting your day.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 2 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <h3>Small Reminders. Lasting Habits.</h3>
        <p>Real change rarely comes from big efforts. It comes from small actions repeated consistently. Every gentle reminder reinforces better posture until it becomes second nature.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 3 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <h3>Designed to Disappear</h3>
        <p>Made from soft, food-grade silicone and weighing only 70 grams, PostureTru sits comfortably beneath your clothing without restricting movement, so your focus stays on your day.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefit 4 -->
      <div class="benefit-card">
        <h3>Works While You Work</h3>
        <p>Whether you're studying, coding, working from home, or gaming for hours, PostureTru quietly monitors your posture in the background. No app to watch. No routine to remember. Just gentle awareness when you need it most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product Benefits",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Heading",
      "default": "Awareness That Stays With You"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "subtitle",
      "label": "Subheading",
      "default": "PostureTru isn't designed to force perfect posture. It's designed to help you notice the exact moment you begin to slouch, so better posture becomes something you naturally return to, day after day."
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
